page.title: 15WEST FELTON TRADE
page.content: WEST FELTON HAS SEVERAL SHOPS AND SMALL BUSINESSES,ALL OF WHICH SEEM TO RUN QUITE SUCCESSFULLY.MR.T.YOUENS HAS A SMALL VILLAGE STORE AT THE SOUTH END OF THE VILLAGE SUPPLYING GENERAL GROCERY AND FROZEN FOODS.MR.&MRS.G.SEABURY RUN THE POST OFFICE AND GENERAL STORE AT THE NORTH END OF THE VILLAGE.APART FROM THE USUAL POST OFFICE BUSINESS SUCH AS STAMPS,PENSIONS,LICENCES ETC.,THEY ALSO SELL GROCERIES,VEGETABLES,FROZEN FOODS AND DAILY AND SUNDAY PAPERS. NEAR THE POST OFFICE IS AN ANTIQUE SHOP THAT DEALS IN THE USUAL RANGE OF SMALL ANTIQUES AND FURNITURE.THE OWNERS OF THE COURT ALSO DEAL IN ANTIQUES,AND BEHIND THE COURT,IN COURT COTTAGE THE OWNER MAKES OBJECTS OUT OF WOOD TO SELL.A GARAGE SELLS PETROL AND VOLVO CARS,ANOTHER GARAGE SELLS SUBARU CARS AND ONE SELLS PETROL AND USED CAR
